data.description: Great opportunity located in the highly desired community of Grove Brook Estates conveniently located on Hwy 90 close to the N Myrtle Beach area for your convenience.  This 3 bedroom 2 bath home is well landscaped yard, with a patio, fenced in backyard, 2 car attached garage,  and a Carolina room.  New carpet and paint job throughout the bedrooms and living area. The master bedroom has a walk in closet, ceiling fan, master bath with new double vanities and luxury vinyl plank flooring.  The seller just replaced all appliances and countertops in the kitchen. This home is  located across the street from Middle School. Wonderful family community with area for boat and trailer storage and also playground. Close to HWY 31 and 22, medical facilities, shopping, restaurants and the beach. Right down the street from the new North Myrtle Beach Recreation Park which has it all for sports, playground, doggie parks, etc. Home makes a wonderful primary residence or rental property.  Square footage is approximate and not guaranteed. The buyer is responsible for all verification.
